{"tid":957351,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美股勁升逾千點　日股承接升勢早段升逾700點　收復2萬點大關","createTime":"2018-12-27T03:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T10:50:43.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b62c77ade72b4ec966af4739da4e3e5de24b2e8","tid":957351,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2253543/org/195a458bfa708acda0f973f48d5c8fda.jpg/rZW5Z7vLhIVz545twlnHRO9ExMZZbzXMEpNL0xKTS9M?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2253543%2Forg%2F195a458bfa708acda0f973f48d5c8fda.jpg%2FrZW5Z7vLhIVz545twlnHRO9ExMZZbzXMEpNL0xKTS9M%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=95b78d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國股市在聖誕後出現大反彈，抽升1086點，以點數計為歷來最大升幅。受到美股上揚帶動，亞太區股市今早紛紛上揚，其中日本股市在早段抽升逾700點，收復2萬點關口。<br />\n<br />\n日經指數今早高開379點後，升勢便隨即擴大，最高見20091點，最新報20060點，升733點；南韓股市今早表現相對較為平淡，高開4點後便回落，最新報2027點，跌不足1點。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲及新西蘭股市在假期後重開，兩者均上揚，澳洲普通股200指數最新報5555點，升61點，新西蘭NZX 20指數最新報5832點，升57點。"},{"pid":"c617b753069cc706161f1c4bbd406eb910b2bbdb","tid":957351,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"681221ddf3264bf8c0b13b0e86f0cd7d26009935","tid":957351,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"又點會估到香港股市會由升轉為跌呢"},{"pid":"bbe693bc8e6f48e8142af1652d92e314091fec7f","tid":957351,"uid":46947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"681221ddf3264bf8c0b13b0e86f0cd7d26009935","tid":957351,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"又點會估到香港股市會由升轉為跌呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"因為港股之前冇跟跌，憑乜撚跟人升。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：誓要殺250大戶牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857882c6a3bbf67a0e34ab6f673f9b741fc9d6ae","tid":957351,"uid":17866,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"681221ddf3264bf8c0b13b0e86f0cd7d26009935","tid":957351,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"又點會估到香港股市會由升轉為跌呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"因為<br />\n美日一體<br />\n港支一體<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}